## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-103">此类型已弃用，将.NET Framework 的未来版本中删除。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-103">This type is deprecated and will be removed in a future version of the .NET Framework.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-104">有关详细信息，请参阅[Oracle 和 ADO.NET](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/oracle-and-adonet.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-104">For more information, see [Oracle and ADO.NET](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/oracle-and-adonet.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-105"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>用作之间的桥梁**数据集**和用于检索和保存数据的数据库。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-105">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> serves as a bridge between a **DataSet** and database for retrieving and saving data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-106"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>通过使用提供此桥<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Fill%2A>将数据加载到数据库中<xref:System.Data.DataSet>，并使用<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>发送中所做的更改<xref:System.Data.DataSet>回数据源。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-106">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> provides this bridge by using <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> to load data from the database into the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, and using <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A> to send changes made in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> back to the data source.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-107">当<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>填充<xref:System.Data.DataSet>，它会创建所需的表和列返回的数据如果它们尚不存在。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-107">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> fills a <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, it creates the necessary tables and columns for the returned data if they do not already exist.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-108">但是，主键信息不包含隐式创建的架构中除非<xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A>属性设置为<xref:System.Data.MissingSchemaAction.AddWithKey>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-108">However, primary key information is not included in the implicitly created schema unless the <xref:System.Data.Common.DataAdapter.MissingSchemaAction%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Data.MissingSchemaAction.AddWithKey>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-109">你还可能<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>创建的架构<xref:System.Data.DataSet>，其中包括主键信息，与使用数据填充它之前<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.FillSchema%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-109">You may also have the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> create the schema of the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, including primary key information, before filling it with data using <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.FillSchema%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-110">有关详细信息，请参阅[将现有约束添加到数据集](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/adding-existing-constraints-to-a-dataset.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-110">For more information, see [Adding Existing Constraints to a DataSet](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/adding-existing-constraints-to-a-dataset.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="af938-111">默认情况下，数值字段导入到<xref:System.Data.DataTable>与<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Fill%2A>映射到<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-111">By default, numeric fields imported to a <xref:System.Data.DataTable> with <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Fill%2A> are mapped to <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-112">可以将溢出<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>，并通过导入是太大或太高精度的非整型数值引发 Oracle 异常，<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>的精度限制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-112">It is possible to overflow the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>, and throw an Oracle exception, by importing a non-integral numeric value that is either too large or too high precision for the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>'s precision limitations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-113">说明，请参阅<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber>有关详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-113">Refer to the description of <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleNumber> for more information.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-114"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>还包括<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>， <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>， <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>， <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A>，并`TableMappings`属性以便于加载和更新的数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-114">The <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> also includes the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.UpdateCommand%2A>, and `TableMappings` properties to facilitate loading and updating of data.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-115">适用于 Oracle 的.NET Framework 数据提供程序不支持批处理的 SQL 语句。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-115">The .NET Framework Data Provider for Oracle does not support batched SQL statements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-116">但是，它的确允许你使用多个`REF CURSOR`输出参数来填充**数据集**，其自身中的每个<xref:System.Data.DataTable>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-116">However, it does allow you to use multiple `REF CURSOR` output parameters to fill a **DataSet**, each in its own <xref:System.Data.DataTable>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-117">必须定义的参数，将其标记为输出参数，并指示它们是`REF CURSOR`数据类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-117">You must define the parameters, mark them as output parameters, and indicate that they are `REF CURSOR` data types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-118">请注意，不能使用<xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A>方法时<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>使用填充`REF CURSOR`参数返回的存储过程，因为 Oracle 不提供表名和列名的是确定所需的信息执行 SQL 语句时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-118">Note that you cannot use the <xref:System.Data.Common.DbDataAdapter.Update%2A> method when the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> is filled using `REF CURSOR` parameters returned by a stored procedure, because Oracle does not provide the information necessary to determine what the table name and column names are when the SQL statement is executed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-119">下面的 C# 示例假定你已创建此存储的过程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-119">The following C# example assumes that you have created this stored procedure.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-120">在 Oracle 服务器上创建以下 Oracle 包。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-120">Create the following Oracle package on the Oracle server.</span></span>  
  
```  
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE CURSPKG AS   
   TYPE T_CURSOR IS REF CURSOR;   
   PROCEDURE OPEN_ONE_CURSOR (N_EMPNO IN NUMBER,   
      IO_CURSOR OUT T_CURSOR);   
   PROCEDURE OPEN_TWO_CURSORS (EMPCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR,   
      DEPTCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR);  
END CURSPKG;  
/  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-121">在 Oracle 服务器上创建下面的 Oracle 包正文。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-121">Create the following Oracle package body on the Oracle server.</span></span>  
  
```  
CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CURSPKG AS   
    PROCEDURE OPEN_ONE_CURSOR (N_EMPNO IN NUMBER,   
                               IO_CURSOR OUT T_CURSOR)   
    IS   
        V_CURSOR T_CURSOR;   
    BEGIN   
        IF N_EMPNO <> 0 THEN   
             OPEN V_CURSOR FOR   
             SELECT EMP.EMPNO, EMP.ENAME, DEPT.DEPTNO, DEPT.DNAME   
                  FROM EMP, DEPT   
                  WHERE EMP.DEPTNO = DEPT.DEPTNO   
                        AND EMP.EMPNO = N_EMPNO;   
        ELSE   
             OPEN V_CURSOR FOR   
             SELECT EMP.EMPNO, EMP.ENAME, DEPT.DEPTNO, DEPT.DNAME   
                  FROM EMP, DEPT   
                  WHERE EMP.DEPTNO = DEPT.DEPTNO;   
        END IF;   
        IO_CURSOR := V_CURSOR;   
    END OPEN_ONE_CURSOR;   
    PROCEDURE OPEN_TWO_CURSORS (EMPCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR,   
                                DEPTCURSOR OUT T_CURSOR)   
    IS   
        V_CURSOR1 T_CURSOR;   
        V_CURSOR2 T_CURSOR;   
    BEGIN   
        OPEN V_CURSOR1 FOR SELECT * FROM EMP;   
        OPEN V_CURSOR2 FOR SELECT * FROM DEPT;   
        EMPCURSOR  := V_CURSOR1;   
        DEPTCURSOR := V_CURSOR2;   
    END OPEN_TWO_CURSORS;   
END CURSPKG;  
 /  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-122">下面的 C# 示例演示如何获取表和列信息使用存储的过程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-122">The following C# example demonstrates how you might obtain table and column information using the stored procedure.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// GetConnectionString() returns a connection string for  
// the data source.  
  
string connString = GetConnectionString();  
DataSet ds = new DataSet();  
OracleConnection conn = new OracleConnection(connString);  
OracleCommand cmd = conn.CreateCommand();  
  
cmd.CommandText = "CURSPKG.OPEN_TWO_CURSORS";  
cmd.CommandType = CommandType.StoredProcedure;  
cmd.Parameters.Add("EMPCURSOR", OracleType.Cursor).Direction =   
       ParameterDirection.Output;  
cmd.Parameters.Add("DEPTCURSOR", OracleType.Cursor).Direction =   
       ParameterDirection.Output;  
  
OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter(cmd);  
da.TableMappings.Add("Table", "Emp");  
da.TableMappings.Add("Table1", "Dept");  
da.Fill(ds);  
  
ds.Relations.Add("EmpDept", ds.Tables["Dept"].Columns["Deptno"],   
      ds.Tables["Emp"].Columns["Deptno"], false);  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-123">下面的 Visual Basic 示例演示如何使用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>来填充<xref:System.Data.DataSet>使用 Oracle `REF CURSOR`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-123">The following Visual Basic example demonstrates how to use an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> to fill a <xref:System.Data.DataSet> using an Oracle `REF CURSOR`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-124">这些示例使用 Oracle Scott/Tiger 架构中定义，并且需要以下 PL/SQL 包和包正文表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-124">These examples use tables that are defined in the Oracle Scott/Tiger schema, and require the following PL/SQL package and package body.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-125">您必须创建这些要使用的示例在服务器上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-125">You must create these on your server to use the examples.</span></span>  
  
