## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-156">当<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>属性分配到以前创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>，则<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>不克隆。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-156">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-157">相反，<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>保留对以前创建的引用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-157">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-158">更新操作期间，如果<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>未设置主键中存在信息时<xref:System.Data.DataSet>，可以使用<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder>类，以自动生成<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>，和对帐所需的其他命令<xref:System.Data.DataSet>到数据库。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-158">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-159">若要执行此操作，设置<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>属性的<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-159">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-160">生成逻辑还要求要中存在的键列信息<xref:System.Data.DataSet>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-160">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-161">有关详细信息请参阅[使用 Commandbuilder 生成命令](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-161">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="af938-162">下面的示例创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>，并设置<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A>和<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-162">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af938-163">它假定你已创建<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af938-163">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  Dim parm As OracleParameter  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn)  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
